<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Paiement Réussi | FORFEO LAB</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body { background-color: #f8f9fa; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; min-height: 100vh; margin: 0; }
        
        .success-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 3rem;
            border-radius: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 90%;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        /* Effet qui bouge au survol */
        .success-card:hover {
            transform: scale(1.02);
        }

        .check-container {
            width: 100px; height: 100px;
            background: #28a745;
            color: white;
            font-size: 50px;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin: 0 auto 2rem;
            animation: bounceIn 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
        }

        @keyframes bounceIn {
            0% { transform: scale(0.3); opacity: 0; }
            50% { transform: scale(1.1); }
            100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 1; }
        }

        .btn-dash {
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            font-weight: bold;
            padding: 12px 30px;
        }
        .btn-dash:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(0,123,255,0.3);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="success-card">
        <div class="check-container">✓</div>
        <h1 class="fw-bold text-dark">Paiement Confirmé !</h1>
        <p class="text-muted fs-5 mb-4">
            Bienvenue dans l'élite. Votre statut **Premium** a été activé automatiquement.
        </p>
        <div class="bg-light p-3 rounded-3 mb-4 text-start">
            <small class="text-uppercase fw-bold text-primary d-block mb-1">Prochaines étapes :</small>
            <ul class="list-unstyled mb-0 small text-dark">
                <li>✅ Accès illimité aux missions</li>
                <li>✅ Réception de l'email de bienvenue</li>
                <li>✅ Support prioritaire activé</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <a href="/entreprise/dashboard" class="btn btn-primary btn-dash rounded-pill w-100">Accéder à mon Dashboard</a>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
